name: Self Portrait During EPROM Reconstruction of the First Biomesh Contagion [Cryptoborg #17]
description:
Zeta works her way through the shattered EPROM struggling to reconstruct the events of the previous twenty-four hours - piecing-together fragments of hidden, protected, and encrypted material.

Functional abnormalities have spread from electronic devices into biological organisms through control-grafts and syncretic-feeds creating a recursive binary biomesh as it spreads. It transmutes from a decentralizing network contagion crossing the barrier between technical machines and organic flesh, spreading rapidly from species to species.
